{"title":"【086】CSS布局之之浮动清理","slug":"hell0-world32","date":"2022-10-24T13:43:27.000Z","updated":"2023-06-21T11:22:08.226Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hell0-world32.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"                flow       <br><br><br>        -->            float:left     ","covers":null,"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"wclassth=device-wclassth, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>flow</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"flow-clear-style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n   <br><br><br>\n   <div class=\"box\">\n     <!--<div class=\"container\">-->\n     <div class=\"a\">\n       float:left\n     </div> <span id=\"more\"></span>\n     <div class=\"b\">\n        float:left\n     </div> \n     <div class=\"c\">\n        float:left\n     </div>\n     <!-- </div>-->\n     <div class=\"d\">\n        float:left\n     </div>\n   </div> \n     若四个元素，前三个都是浮动，第四个不是，<!--则在前三个前添加父元素。<br><br><br><br><br><br>\n    普通元素，子元素大小可以将父元素撑开，但浮动元素未占据空间则不能将父元素撑开。故需为父元素设置高度<br><br>\n    为使父元素高度保持正常，需给父元素增加样式：第一种overflow: auto;对于超出边界的元素，父元素可自动调整<br><br>\n   第二种-->添加clear属性，可清除浮动 ，不想当前元素受到前面最近元素影响，就给当前元素添加clear中的: left/both/right;<br><br>\n  <br><br><br>\n</body>\n</html>","categories":[{"name":"CSS","slug":"CSS","count":30,"path":"api/categories/CSS.json"}],"tags":[]}